"Ifoni yakho ibishisa kakhulu, ngakho-ke yacisha ukuze iphole. Ifoni yakho manje isebenza ngokuvamile.

Ifoni yakho ingashisa kakhulu uma:
 • Usebenzisa izinhlelo zokusebenza ezinkulu (njegegeyimu, ividiyo, noma ama-app okufuna)
 • Landa noma layisha amafayela amakhulu
 • Sebenzisa ifoni yakho kumazinga okushisa aphezulu"

"Idivayisi yakho ibishisa kakhulu, ngakho-ke yacisha ukuze iphole. Idivayisi yakho manje isebenza ngokuvamile.

Idivayisi yakho ingashisa kakhulu uma:
 • Usebenzisa ama-app wensiza enamandla (njegegeyimu, ividiyo, noma ama-app wokufuna)
 • Dawuniloda noma layisha amafayela amakhulu
 • Sebenzisa idivayisi yakho kumazinga wokushisa aphezulu"

"Ithebulethi yakho ibishisa kakhulu, ngakho-ke yacisha ukuze iphole. Ithebulethi yakho manje isebenza ngokuvamile.
